name: Peace of S-ETH ?
description:
This artwork comes from our naive contemplation. When ETH becomes the top tier in NFT art, then people struggle for alms and are tricked into selling their assets in real life for what they call as a "gas fees," even though other blockchains provide some of the same opportunities, and when generative arts are considered something pop and trash, this part happens. We are willing to forget our mother and the environment for something that is not real, which will not last forever. All will fade, evaporate, then disappear. And this is Peace of  S-ETH. Maybe it's me, him, or them, or even you.
